                    <span>Dr. Skiffington's coaching books have become industry standard materials throughout the global coaching community and make valuable reference resources for any coaching program. This book is the first text that provides practical steps in applying the model of coaching while her elite coach training courses (via Behavioral Coaching Institute) show you how to select and master the appropriate methodology, tools and processes for your practice.</span>
                  
              
